                           <p>Several lacunas.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Margins too closely cut, but some catchwords have been preserved.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Some of the upper margins have been water-damaged.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        </condition>
                     
                     
                     
                     </supportDesc>
                     
                     
                     
